Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.03,0:25:16.97,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}都如此闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.38,0:25:23.36,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是你惹怒我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.13,0:25:27.48,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两人吵架的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.57,0:25:33.89,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}还是我惹哭你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.87,0:25:38.99,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手足无措的时候
