Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.32,0:27:02.74,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}以及你用双手轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.42,0:27:07.78,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱住我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.41,0:27:15.49,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}街道都微笑着
