Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.31,0:29:04.84,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我今天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.46,0:29:10.67,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也只是远远地凝视你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.36,0:29:16.48,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使时日已久
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.72,0:29:24.81,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仍然不知你名姓
