Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.83,0:29:47.19,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}发辫轻轻摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.83,0:29:53.02,song_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比起往常
